name: SkyFight - The First Real Operation
description:
SkyFight - The First Real Operation is a game that shows the first time that the Delta Squadron participated in a real battle, fighting an enemy that has dangerous objectives! 

SkyFight is an arcade airplane game that contains one mission, an idea of a universe that can be expanded!
